author: Kaitlan Collins
title: Obama Cracks Joke About Being A Lame Duck Within Minutes Of Starting Farewell Speech
text:
TOP 5415987 
Barack Obama cracked a joke about being a lame duck president within minutes of starting his farewell speech. 
As the president took the stage at the McCormick Place in Chicago Tuesday night, he acknowledged that he only has a few days left in office. 
“You can tell that I’m a lame duck because no one’s following instructions,” Obama said.
